features: 【Wide Compatibility】This dishwasher circulation pump assembly is compatible with GE WD26x23258 dishwasher circulation pump, and replaces part number WD26X22285, WD26X22518, WD26X22826, WD26X23258, AP6039424, 4466766, PS11772000.

【Dishwasher Fitment】Compatible with most dishwashers including ADT521PGJ0BS ADT521PGJ0BS ADT521PGJ0BS ADT521PGJ0WS ADT521PGJ0WS ADT521PGJ0WS ADT521PGJ2BS ADT521PGJ2WS CDT706P2M4S1 CDT706P2M4S1 CDT706P2M5S1 CDT725SSF7SS CDT725SSF7SS CDT805P2N0S1 CDT805P2N0S1 CDT805P2N0S1 CDT805P2N0S1 CDT835SMJ0DS CDT835SMJ0DS CDT835SMJ2DS CDT835SMJ2DS CDT835SMJ4DS CDT835SMJ5DS CDT835SMJ5DS CDT835SSJ0SS CDT835SSJ0SS CDT835SSJ2SS CDT835SSJ2SS CDT835SSJ4SS CDT835SSJ5SS

【When You Need to Replace Pump】You need to replace your broken circulation pump, when your dishwasher have such problems as following: The water flow pipe isn't hot despite the pump running; A water leak coming from the pump; The pump is making unusual noises; The pump casing feels hot; Some or all of your radiators aren't heating up;You have no hot water.

【Excellent Function】This dishwasher circulation pump circulates the water in the dishwasher and cleans dirty dishes. Having a dishwasher that works properly avoids hand washing or dishes not clean, and you can enjoy a pleasant after-dinner time with your family while the dishwasher is working.
【Outstanding Feature】Dishwasher circulation pump is made of high quality materials with durable and sturdy performance, installation with five clamps, not easy to loose and leak.

【100% Satisfaction Guarantee】If you have any questions about our WD26X23258 dishwasher circulation pump, please contact us at first time. We support refund within 30-Day guarantee, 12-Month warranty for quality-related issues.

reviews.reviewText: Seams to work well but during install the plug did not fit and had to be modified- the plug ridges were opposite. This was fixed with a drimel to grind a relief onto one side. This motor has a whine to it and is much louder then OEM. We are on day one of use time will tell if it works.
